snippet.title: Hyper Torque Racing for Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Be the wind on the circuit! A real racer experience with simple visuals! 
That's "Hyper Torque Racing"
Hyper Torque Racing is a racing game for Nintendo Switch.
It is now available. Please give it a try.

Offical Website: https://hypertorqueracing.com/
Twitter : https://twitter.com/HyperTrqRacing
